---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="About Dannie Waldén"
	pubDate={new Date('2026-06-28')}
>
	<p>
		Dannie Waldén writes long-form essays on software design — event sourcing,
		vertical slice architecture, model-first practice, and how agentic AI is
		reshaping the way software gets built.
	</p>

	<p>
		Essays land in series. The first is
		<a href="/series/noboundedcontexts/"><em>NoBoundedContexts</em></a>,
		arguing that the solution-space side of strategic DDD has nothing
		structural left to do inside an event-sourced, vertical-sliced,
		model-first monolith.
	</p>
</Layout>
